### Create Root Category
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Category",
  "slug": "test-category",
  "image-url": "https://example.com/images/test.jpg",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "display-order": 99
}

###

### Create Root Category - DRAFT status (default)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Draft Category",
  "slug": "draft-category"
}

###

### Create Subcategory (with parent)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Subcategory",
  "slug": "test-subcategory",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "display-order": 1,
  "parent-id": 1
}

###

### Create Category - Duplicate slug (expects error)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Duplicate Slug",
  "slug": "electronics"
}

###

### Create Category - Missing required fields (expects validation error)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###

### Create Category - Invalid parent (expects 404)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Orphan Category",
  "slug": "orphan-category",
  "parent-id": 9999
}
